{"tid":712754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(人間慘劇)比假口供竟獲放生！？","createTime":"2018-06-22T10:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T14:08:49.000Z","uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bce88abe70bf80665b88643de851ac8efd29d893","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20427999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427999&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1292bf1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427999&h=7ca95fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20427999</a><br />\n<br />\n警不起訴　孖女證供無呈堂<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】女被告王榮汶的孖女曾於案發後被警方拘捕，更向警方招認是父母教唆她們夾口供，又自言曾與母親用藤條打林林。警方曾考慮一併控告孖女，但經諮詢律政司指示後，最終未有落案起訴；她們的證供亦因此被列作「未用於檢控的資料」（unused material），從未在審訊中呈堂，直至王的代表大狀昨求情時引述，才在庭上曝光。<br />\n<br />\n大孖認打林　細孖不記得<br />\n<br />\n據知王在調查期間非常不合作，而且經常情緒激動，警方遂改向孖女問話。孖女起初仍與女被告口徑一致，堅稱林林天生殘障，一直卧床，及後才向警方招認是父母教她們作供。<br />\n大孖供稱曾與母親用藤條打林林，自此林林不肯進食，身體狀況越來越差，體弱到只能卧床。此時母親害怕別人以為她虐打女兒，不敢求醫。惟當大孖其後得悉有緘默權後，便不肯再說下去。細孖向警方承認說謊，惟當警方再問下去，她便堅稱不記得發生過甚麼事，令警方無法進一步了解實情。據了解，警方曾考慮一併控告涉作假證供的孖女，惟諮詢律政司意見後，因她們當時年僅15歲，加上考慮到在案中角色，決定不起訴，令孖女證供未能呈堂。<br />\n大律師陸偉雄回應《蘋果》查詢指，控方若要使用「未用於檢控的資料」，便需傳召相關證人出庭作供，惟控方也要考慮資料的證據價值，以及證人會否「掉轉槍頭」。辯方若要使用該等資料，也同樣要傳召證人出庭。據悉，王一度堅持要傳召孖女出庭，最終放棄。<br />\n■記者楊家樂<br />\n<br />\n相關案情link:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20427906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427906&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d780d006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427906&h=29da2d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20427906</a>"},{"pid":"bf4ad362b8f09903b5bb2467ff9d3e52ea762447","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"起底組要蒲頭喇！"},{"pid":"8cbbc2643e5ab7d1214fcfdf4f4d4b6f1a309f27","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a8c25676851ec3d872baf4f7573c76a46c8d0ef","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"點解可以無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a1bad8dbe5580b3bef70e1acbc9d68f35c20a8","tid":712754,"uid":63243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲要問律政司"},{"pid":"e1dd710324fc52e3ff09a2690ebeaceb0c683fa9","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a1bad8dbe5580b3bef70e1acbc9d68f35c20a8","tid":712754,"uid":63243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲要問律政司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"律政司大撚曬，連法律都行埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b39f2b87c84e2f0e752cf0f301a5c87642485b6","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"放生疑犯法財仔職員 法官轟：「我做Bar（大律師）31年都冇聽過」「律政司係無敵㗎！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/712743/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/712743/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd33c4bddd4e6b626fd4302c8b438067a36cf871","tid":712754,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"蝗禍都冇人理，我諗我都係放棄連燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji